<Rain>
  I'm raining.

  Nourishing my body  
  with tears of joy  
  and peace.  

  Crystallizing jewel drops of life  
  from the expansiveness  
  of my breath.

  I'm shining.  
  Rays of love descend  
  from my eyes,  
  flowing into my heart,  
  warming my body  
  from within.
</Rain>